<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?xml-model href="../../schema/HBAS_letters.odd.rng" type="application/xml" schematypens="http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="L041403.xml" xml:base="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/schnitzler/bahrschnitzler/letters" prev="L041529.html" next="T030085.html"><teiHeader type="text"><fileDesc><titleStmt><title level="s">Hermann Bahr – Arthur Schnitzler: Briefwechsel, Aufzeichnungen, Dokumente 1891–1931</title><title level="a">Theodor Herzl an Arthur Schnitzler, 8. 12. 1893</title><title type="iso-date" n="01">1893-12-08</title><author ref="#pmb11673">Herzl, Theodor</author><editor><name>Ifkovits, Kurt</name><name>Müller, Martin Anton</name></editor><funder><name>FWF - Fonds für Wissenschaft und Forschung</name><address><street>Sensengasse 1</street><postCode>1090 Wien</postCode><placeName><country>A</country><settlement>Wien</settlement></placeName></address></funder></titleStmt><editionStmt><edition>HBAS</edition><respStmt><resp>Transkription und Kommentierung</resp><name>Kurt Ifkovits</name><name>Martin Anton Müller</name></respStmt></editionStmt><publicationStmt><publisher>Theatermuseum, Wien</publisher><idno type="HBAS-L" n="403"/><availability status="free"><p>Copyright © 2017</p></availability><idno type="handle">https://hdl.handle.net/21.11115/0000-000E-8704-5</idno></publicationStmt><seriesStmt><p>Machine-Readable Transcriptions of the Correspondence between Hermann Bahr and Arthur Schnitzler</p></seriesStmt><sourceDesc><correspDesc><sender><persName ref="#pmb11673">Herzl, Theodor</persName></sender><addressee><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName></addressee><placeSender><placeName ref="#pmb182">Paris</placeName></placeSender><placeAddressee><placeName ref="#pmb50">[Wien]</placeName></placeAddressee><dateSender><date when="1893-12-08" n="01">8. 12. 1893</date></dateSender><context/></correspDesc><listBibl><biblStruct><monogr><author ref="#pmb11673">Herzl, Theodor</author><title level="m">Briefe und autobiographische Notizen. 1866–1895</title><editor>Bearbeitet von Johannes Wachten</editor><imprint><pubPlace>Berlin, Frankfurt am Main, Wien</pubPlace><publisher>Propyläen</publisher><date when="1983">1983</date></imprint><biblScope unit="pp">541–542</biblScope></monogr></biblStruct></listBibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage></profileDesc><revisionDesc status="candidate"><change who="MAM" when="2016-01-26">Angelegt aus Scan</change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs>, le <date>8 Dez<supplied>ember</supplied> 1893</date></dateline><salute>Lieber Freund!</salute></opener><p>Sieben Wochen war ich malariakrank – aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb462">Venedig</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb898">Toulon</rs> mitgebracht –, schwere Fieberwochen. Heute ein zermatschgerter Reconvalescent. So fasse ich mich nothgedrungen kurz. Ich gratulire zur <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29823">Märchenaufführung</rs>. Die Bühne ist erobert. Sie werden sie nicht mehr verlassen. Nur sich treu bleiben! u. ringsherum reden lassen.</p><closer>Ich grüsse Sie herzlich<lb/>Ihr aufrichtig ergebener <signed>Herzl</signed></closer><postscript><p>Könnten Sie mir <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10815">Bahrs</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL403-1"/><rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb30271">Artikelserie über Jung-Oesterreich</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL403-1h"><p><bibl><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10815">Hermann Bahr</rs>: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb30271">Das junge Oesterreich</rs>. In: <rs type="org" ref="#pmb29424">Deutsche Zeitung</rs>, Jg. 23, Teil 1: Nr. 7806, <date>20. 9. 1893</date>, Morgen-Ausgabe, S. 1–2; Teil 2: Nr. 7813, <date>27. 9. 1893</date>, Morgen-Ausgabe, S. 1–3, <ptr target="T030009"/>; Teil 3: Nr. 7823, <date>7. 10. 1893</date>, Morgen-Ausgabe, S. 1–3</bibl>.</p></note> (<rs type="org" ref="#pmb29424">Deutsche Zeitung</rs>) verschaffen? Bitte!</p></postscript></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb11673"><persName><forename>Theodor</forename><surname>Herzl</surname></persName><birth><date when="1860-05-02">02.05.1860</date><settlement ref="#pmb43471"><placeName type="pref">Budapest</placeName><location><geo>47,49835 19,04045</geo></location></settlement></birth><death><date when="1904-07-03">03.07.1904</date><settlement ref="#pmb470"><placeName type="pref">Edlach</placeName><location><geo>47,69255 15,80915</geo></location></settlement></death><sex value="male"/><occupation ref="#pmb90">Schriftsteller/Schriftstellerin</occupation><occupation ref="#pmb99">Journalist/Journalistin</occupation><idno type="URL" subtype="schnitzler-tagebuch">https://schnitzler-tagebuch.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/entity/person_16165</idno><idno type="URL" subtype="d-nb">https://d-nb.info/gnd/118550241</idno><idno type="URL" subtype="bahrschnitzler">https://bahrschnitzler.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/entity/pmb11673</idno><idno type="URL" subtype="pmb">https://pmb.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/entity/11673</idno><idno type="URL" subtype="schnitzler-briefe">https://schnitzler-briefe.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/pages/hits.html?searchkey=pmb11673</idno><idno type="URL" subtype="schnitzler-lektueren">https://schnitzler-lektueren.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/pmb11673.html</idno></person><person xml:id="pmb2121"><persName><forename>Arthur</forename><surname>Schnitzler</surname></persName><birth><date when="1862-05-15">15.05.1862</date><settlement ref="#pmb50"><placeName type="pref">Wien</placeName><location><geo>48,2066 16,37341</geo></location></settlement></birth><death><date when="1931-10-21">21.10.1931</date><settlement ref="#pmb50"><placeName type="pref">Wien</placeName><location><geo>48,2066 16,37341</geo></location></settlement></death><sex value="male"/><occupation ref="#pmb90">Schriftsteller/Schriftstellerin</occupation><occupation ref="#pmb97">Mediziner/Medizineri